verbs.description: The force [V: might] have been with ABC on May 4 , but interest in the U.S. labor market certainly was n’t . That night World News Tonight with David Muir spent a meager 15 seconds announcing the April jobs report which showed the lowest unemployment rate since 2000 . That 3.9 percent was what other journalists called a “ wow number ” that could even help re - elect President Donald Trump .
